objects.query: SELECT Id, FirstName, LastName, PersonEmail, Phone, PersonMobilePhone, DateOfBirth__pc, Gender__pc, RecordTypeId FROM Account WHERE Recordtype.DeveloperName = 'PeanutsGang' ORDER BY Name
